<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_448" id="223v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_448_r1l1">Claſen <expan>Holcʒing<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>vvıſe<ex>n</ex>pruk</expan> <expan>geſeʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_448_r1l2"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Holcʒing<ex>er</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l3">vogts <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü Liechtenaw / . Darvmb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l4"><expan>heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒe red geſacʒt / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l5">hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ er <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> handlung nichts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l6">wıſʒe / . vnd er wölle ſeinen vogt beſenden / daʒ </ab>
