<del rend="strikethrough"> gen <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l8">cʒü vns kum vnd das <expan>verantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / . Wolt Jr nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l9"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> yemands dar cʒü <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das mügt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l10">Jr wol tün / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Tyb<ex>ur</ex>cıȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_448_r1l11"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Jm Steinhaws <expan>kuſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l12">cʒü Onelſpach / <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_448" id="223v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Clasen <expan>Holczing<ex>er</ex></expan>, czü
                            <expan>Wise<ex>n</ex>pruk</expan>
<expan>gesezze<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Holczing<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des vogts <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        czü Liechtenaw, darumb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumel,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan> cze red gesaczt und
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>,
                        daz er <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> handlung nichts wisze, und er wölle seinen vogt
                        besenden, daz er <app><note><q type="date">auf den <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mitwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></q>20.04.1412</note></app> herein czü uns kum und das
                                <expan>verantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. Wolt ir nu
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> yemands darczü
                            <expan>schicke<ex>n,</ex></expan> das mügt ir wol tün.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Tyb<ex>ur</ex>cii.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> im Steinhaws,
                            <expan>kust<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Onelspach
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
